    "The query returned 236 tools that were manually analysed.",
    "Similar to the analysis of the papers, this process was conducted in two phases.",
    "Initially, the first author selected a preliminary set of 45 tools based solely on their descriptions in the repository.",
    "Next, all authors evaluated these tools by examining their websites, tutorials, and the tools themselves.",
    "When necessary, the first author collected additional information through interviews with the developers."
